bundle reconstruction result, checksum result, or other verification result
applies only to the declared files, profiles, inputs, corpora, contexts, schemas,
and verification boundary associated with that result.

Modified files, changed rules, changed profiles, changed contexts, changed corpora,
changed schemas, changed evidence, or changed verification artifacts require their
own verification.

Redistribution, modification, or use of the covered materials must not imply
